'''Anne''' is the girlfriend of [[Alice Bickham]].

==History==
When Alice got the call that she needed to come out to [[Seattle]] to confirm DNR on her mother so they could remove the tube and allow her to die, Anne came with her and supported her as she said goodbye to her mother and sat while she took her last breaths.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is dating [[Alice Bickham]]. Their relationship is serious enough that Anne came to Seattle with Alice when her mother was dying.
